1.12
log
@reduce more .Nd to one line and kill more .Tn
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: rfx.4,v 1.11 2011/09/03 22:59:07 jmc Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 2004, Miodrag Vallat.
.\" All rights reserved.
.\"
.\" Redistribution and use in source and binary forms, with or without
